data.description: Excellent opportunity for first time buyers, this 3 bed/2 bath single family home in a large corner lot 9,316 Sq. ft. with enough space for pool, RV, boat, large terrace or to grow your family.  Plenty of parking space.  New roof 2023, circular driveway, impact windows and doors.  New Storage house. Highly desirable neighborhood just blocks away from the famous Hard Rock Stadium just 1.6 miles away, you will have front-row access to all the major sporting events and concerts. FHA/VA/CONV Financing. HOA and No flood Ins. needed.
